Delcatty (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0300: Skitty
Pokémon
#0302: Sableye →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Delcatty (TCG Pocket).

Delcatty has been featured on 14 different cards since it debuted in the EX Ruby & Sapphire expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Delcatty cards are normally Colorless-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Delcatty

Delcatty
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
